headline: Should You Forget Pfizer and Buy This Magnificent Dividend Stock Instead?
summary: One of the big reasons to like Pfizer (NYSE: PFE) today is its huge 7.1% dividend yield.  Pfizer competitor Merck (NYSE: MRK) is yielding a little more than 4%, yet dividend investors will probably be better off with Merck.  While Pfizer's dividend yield is clearly much higher than Merck's, both have relatively attractive yields today.
